篇待定稿后除非版本有较大的调整，一般不会更新这两篇的内容。后两篇将基于kafka-0.8版本进行介绍，后续更新会相对平凡。","categories":[{"name":"kakfa","slug":"kakfa","permalink":"https://it-bo.github.io/categories/kakfa/"}],"tags":[{"name":"learnbook","slug":"learnbook","permalink":"https://it-bo.github.io/tags/learnbook/"},{"name":"kafka","slug":"kafka","permalink":"https://it-bo.github.io/tags/kafka/"}]},{"title":"github博客的第一天","slug":"first-day","date":"2017-01-23T04:58:15.034Z","updated":"2017-02-13T14:40:52.725Z","comments":true,"path":"2017/01/23/first-day/","link":"","permalink":"https://it-bo.github.io/2017/01/23/first-day/","excerpt":"","text":"泡坛多年，一直没有时间整理自己的学习笔记。今年下定决心开始写写博客，只为自己做个技术沉淀。 在博客框架选材上折腾了几天，今天终于在github上把博客搭建好了。特此纪念一下！","categories":[{"name":"学习笔记","slug":"学习笔记","permalink":"https://it-bo.github.io/categories/学习笔记/"}],"tags":[{"name":"learnbook","slug":"learnbook","permalink":"https://it-bo.github.io/tags/learnbook/"}]}]}